#

Creamy Shrimp and Corn Chowder

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

ChowderSeafoodComfort Food

Description

A rich and hearty chowder featuring succulent shrimp, sweet corn, and a creamy base, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 pound, peeled and deveined
  • Corn kernels: 2 cups, fresh or frozen
  • Diced potatoes: 2 cups
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Thyme: 1 teaspoon, dried
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
